title: Alcatel Switches: Chassis Components
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/alcatel
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This Check Monitors the

 - oper

 - alarm

 - admin

 states in Alcatel switches.

 It raises {CRIT}

 - if the component enters an Alarm state.

 - if the Operstate changes to "failed" or "out of serrvices"

 - if the Adminstate changes to "diagnose" or "operate switch"

 There is a {WARN} in case of

 - "booting"

 - "diagnosing"

 - "upgrade"

 - "downgrade"

 No Configuration is needed.

 The check uses the ALCATEL-IND1-TIMETRA-CHASSIS-MIB.

item:
 The name of the device.

inventory:
 One service is created for each active device.

